Explore the caves in the Belize rainforest, find a tour guide and go tubing or zip-lining, visit the rescued animals in the Belize Zoo, or tour the historic museums. There is something for everyone in Belize City.', 'Belize is beautiful and known for its colorful diversity in its natural ecosystems, animals on the gorgeous land, and bright blue water.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f7406cd77b37db_belize-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f74056207b37d6_belize-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/belize-about-banner.jpg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f74086ac7b37da_belize-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f7407b8b7b37d4_belize-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f740225e7b37d7_belize-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f7401ba87b37d5_belize-getting.jpeg','<p id="">The best way to get around Belize City is with a rental car. In Belize City, you will find plenty of local auto rental companies and a few international ones. If you stay for a longer time in Belize, you can get a discount on the rental car.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f7400b917b37d9_belize-fnb.jpeg','<p id="">Belize City cuisine is perhaps best known for its seafood! The beautiful country widely offers fresh fish, lobster, and conch. Tropical fruits are ab-undant and include such delicacies as mangoes, papayas, pineapples, melons, and bananas. Rice and beans are also popular across Belize and are included in most dishes as it is a Caribbean nation.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d09e23f74034a27b37d8_belize-facts.jpeg','<p id="">Belize City has the only Jaguar Preserve in the world.	Belize City uses speed bumps rather than using traffic lights.	Belizean money is very similar to American cash, also known as dollars.	It is the cultural center of the country and offers a large number of interesting cultural attractions.	Four bridges link the different sections of the city: the Swing Bridge, the Chetumal Street Bridge, the BelCan Bridge, and the BelChina Bridge.	Chartering a boat is one of the best ways to explore Belize waters and make the most of your available dive time.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Attraction Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia 