&nbsp;', 'In a country that is quite young compared to the rest of the world, Boston is one of the oldest United States cities, with a breadth of history, elegance, and intellect. Boston is known for its traditional East Coast seafood, like lobster rolls and clam chowder, and good old-fashioned American pies with berries freshly picked from local farms. Come during the fall to see the vivid reds, oranges, and greens of a classic New England autumn. Regardless, during whichever season you visit, you are guaranteed to fall in love with the museums, shopping districts, and markets of this colonial city.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d841a3a38b3be_boston-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0697d5d84627038b3d5_boston-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/boston-massachusetts-.mp4', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d8457ea38b3c1_boston-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d84522138b3bb_boston-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d8477c738b3bc_boston-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d84792338b3c0_boston-getting.jpeg','<p id="">The Boston Public Transportation System comprises an extensive series of metro, trollies, light rail, and buses that ferry the public around Boston safely and cheaply. Taxis are also widely available, but can be more expensive. Like most other major cities, rideshare apps are also quite popular among visitors.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d84781a38b3bf_boston-food.jpeg','<p id="">If you like to sample local cuisine when you visit a city, definitely try a plate of Boston’s oysters, or fresh-caught lobster and blueberry ice cream. Regional favorites make up only a small part of Boston’s gastronomy; Caribbean, Vietnamese, and Cuban food are just a few of its international specialties. There’s an Irish pub on practically every corner where locals come to hang out, as the cuisine here is as much about the experience as it is about the food and drink.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0687d5d84269638b3bd_boston-facts.jpeg','<p id="">The first American lighthouse was built in Boston Harbor, as well as the first subway, and Boston is home to the oldest public park in the United States.Boston is a very walkable city; as of 2020, 16.2% of all Boston citizens walked to work, which is the biggest percentage in the USA.Apartments here aren’t cheap; but not without reason; Boston consistently reports a high satisfaction of living.The city is also considered a leader in innovation, with over 5,000 company startups over the last decade.From 1659 to 1681, the Puritan settlers banned Christmas, feeling that the purpose of the holiday was being forgotten among all the celebrations, but you wouldn’t be able to tell from the general spirit of festivity that seems to take over Boston all throughout the holiday season.The Fig Newton was invented in Boston and named after a Boston Suburb.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut eni