If you take the friendliness of the midwest with the sophistication of New York City, you’d get Buffalo; NYC’s less overwhelming sibling on the other side of the state. Buffalo sits on the eastern side of Lake Erie, just across the border of Ontario, Canada, and is a short drive from Niagara Falls; one of the most famous waterfalls on the globe.&nbsp;This evolving city boasts a dynamic art scene, a massive city parks system, and one of the best American food cities for all budgets.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0691bf36a6cdb3e9d75_buffalo-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0691bf36a1f4f3e9d71_buffalo-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/buffalo-about-banner.jpg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0691bf36a11f43e9d70_buffalo-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0691bf36a44f83e9d76_buffalo-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0681bf36ad5503e9d6d_buffalo-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['',''], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0691bf36a12f53e9d79_worcester_red_sox_at_buffalo_bisons_-_20220731_-_02_-_charlie_the_butcher.jpeg','<p id="">Buffalo wings, craft beer, and pizza; if you want some classic late-night American specialties, you’ll be more than satisfied here. One Buffalo specialty is thebeef-on-weck: a roast beef sandwich served on a salted roll with caraway seeds sprinkled on top.If you’re looking to expand your palette, go to a food bazaar for migrant-owned shops with international tastes. Don’t knock sponge candy until you’ve tried it, and snack your way through bistros and taverns throughout the city.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0681bf36a47893e9d6