&nbsp;', 'Kilimanjaro is a region in Tanzania. The regional capital is the municipality of Moshi. According to the 2012 national census, the region had a population of over 1.6 million. The area is home to the beautiful and iconic snowcapped Mount Kilimanjaro, famous throughout the world. People come from everywhere to climb the peak and enjoy the beautiful landscapes.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6ed5c6f27d80_kilimanjaro-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6e240af27d82_kilimanjaro-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/Kilimanjaro,%20Tanzania%20(City).mp4', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6e92d0f27d7d_kilimanjaro-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6e5b50f27d7b_kilimanjaro-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6e8428f27d7f_kilimanjaro-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6e4411f27d7e_kilimanjaro-getting.jpeg','<p id="">If you plan to climb Kilimanjaro, be sure to secure a licensed guide. You can do this before or after you hit the ground. Park entry and camping/hut fees are around $100 US Dollars per day. You can book an all-inclusive trip from anywhere between $800 and $5,000. Be sure to tip your guides, cooks, and porters.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6e4e48f27d7c_kilimanjaro-food.jpeg','<p id="">The food options will depend upon the package you choose for climbing the mountain. The more expensive, the better the food. However, even with the more expensive tours, the food can get stale and less tasty towards the end of the journey. The cooks will also vary by tour company, and this will impact the flavor and quality to some degree.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08198ae6eebeef27d81_kilimanjaro-facts.jpeg','<p id="">1. Mount Kilimanjaro is the tallest mountain on the African continent and the highest free-standing mountain in the world.2. The oldest person ever to summit Mt. Kilimanjaro was 87-year-old Frenchman Valtee Daniel.3. Almost every kind of ecological system is found on the mountain: cultivated land, rain forest, heath, moorland, alpine desert, and an arctic summit.4. Approximately 25,000 people attempt to reach the summit Mt. Kilimanjaro annually. Approximately two-thirds are successful.5. The most recent volcanic activity was about 200 years ago; the last major eruption was 360,000 years ago.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Attraction Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo con