Managua has an urban feel that sets the pace for the rest of the country. Hikes, zip lines, historical monuments, and outdoor markets are just some of the activities you can fill your days with here.&nbsp;Visit Revolution Plaza and step inside history at the Palace of Culture. Most of all, Managua is a hub of biodiversity. A freshwater lake with bull sharks and turquoise water. Mountains made up of hardened volcanoes. Miles and miles of green forest. You haven’t seen a true downpour until you experience Nicaraguan thunderstorms. Even if you aren’t a fan of wet climates; you have the rain to thank for infusing the land with color.

&nbsp;', 'Test your Spanish skills in the capital city of Central America’s best-kept secret. Between the volcanic coastlines and diverse rainforests of Nicaragua, nestled on the shore of Lake Managua, you’ll find its namesake; the second largest city in the subcontinent. Managua bursts with a diverse culture that mere descriptions can’t do justice.

Live like a true islander, splashing around tropical lagoons and scaling palm trees. Or if you prefer old Spanish architecture and cobblestone streets to sunny beaches, discover the nation’s finest cultural landmarks in the city center. Managua provides the best of both worlds for the most adventurous of travelers.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08c23f74070a97b3793_managua-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08b23f7403dc97b378d_managua-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/managua-about-banner.jpg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08b23f7402ce57b378c_managua-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08b23f740d0977b3790_managua-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08b23f740043b7b378b_managua-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['',''], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08b23f74016387b378e_managua-fnb.jpeg','<p id="">At its humble beginnings, Managua was a quaint fishing village. As such, its residents take advantage of their close proximity to the lake as well as the Pacific and Caribbean coastlines and enjoy fresh fish in their diets. In Nicaragua, lunch is the biggest meal of the day; you can expect to often see grilled meats, corn tortillas, rice, cabbage, beans, and fried plantains as staples, as well as the freshest tropical fruit around! If you’re craving Western fast food, don’t worry; they have that here too! If you prefer eating out, this city won’t wear out your wallet. And being an international city, Managua also offers options from all over the globe, with restaurants specializing in Asian, Middle Eastern, and European cuisine.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08b23f740d9837b378f_managua-facts.jpeg','<p id="">Managua lies between the two other notable cities of Leon and Granada.Nicaraguan history can be dated back to 12000 BC. Managua, founded by the Spanish in 1811 following its Aztec predecessors; contains archeological finds on the lake that go back 2000 years. The name Managua, derived from the indigenous Nahuatl peoples, means ‘surrounded by water’. Agricultural exports are the primary economic contributor, in a city nearing two million residents. As the capital, Managua represents the economic and cultural center of Nicaragua, sustaining most of the national universities, major banks, and tourist attractions. Climate hereis tropical (hot and humid), with a drier season in November-May.Changing leadership brought state unrest during the Nicaraguan revolution in 1979 and the US-backed Contra War of the 80s. National infrastructure took a devastating blow, but massive reconstruction efforts eventually gave Managua the ability to regain its footing in the economy. Now, colorful street art and vibrant nightlife give the city a distinctly metropolitan vibe.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupi