The county is beautiful and iconic in its own way. With miles of sandy beaches, boardwalks, and piers, there is no shortage of vacation spots or destination getaways. Stop in for a stroll down Huntington Beach, stop over at Knotts’s Berry Farm, or an entire week in Anaheim to enjoy the Disney experience. There is more than enough to get your adventurous spirit into gear and still get a chance to relax and enjoy the magnificent sunsets of California.&nbsp;', 'Orange County is one of the most beautiful places in the world. With its perfect weather, stunning beaches and amazing attractions, it’s no wonder that this place is a popular tourist destination. There is so much to see and do in Orange County, from taking in the sights at world-famous theme parks to soaking up the sun on the beach. And with so many great restaurants and shops, you’ll never be bored. California Dreamin’ comes all in one giant package right here in Orange County:&nbsp;a destination with unmatched adventure and attractions.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07370feea465f3db6f3_cancun-c1_0.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07370feea9e233db6f4_cancun-c2_0.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/227215.jpeg', ARRAY['','',''], ARRAY['','<p id="">This may seem obvious, but a car is really the best way to navigate such a vast destination. The locals rely heavily on ridesharing opportunities such as Uber and Lyft. For affordable travel use the OCTA (Orange County Bus Line), where blind users ride for free, or AmTrak also makes stops in various cities in the county. Laguna Beach offers a trolley service within city limits. Taxi services are available if none of the above suit your needs.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07370feea1e6c3db6f2_cancun-fnb_0.jpeg','<p id="">Dive right into this county’s wide array of food and drinks, inspired by countries from around the world. From farm-fresh California cuisine to exotic international flavors, there’s no shortage of great food and drink options in this sunny Southern California region. For a true taste of the OC, head to one of the many farmers markets peppered throughout the county. Here, you’ll find fresh fruits and vegetables, artisanal cheeses, locally-made jams and sauces, and much more. Or, for a more casual dining experience, try one of the many great burger joints or seafood shacks dotting the landscape. Vegan and vegetarian options are plentiful in Orange County as well if you are looking for something for veggie lovers.</p>'], ARRAY['','<p id="">This county is a haven for surfers and beachgoers and is the spot for six of the most famous California towns, most of which are located along the Pacific Coast Highway. Newport Beach, Dana Point, Seal Beach, Huntington Beach, San Clemente, and Laguna Beach, are all major beach towns with attractions that range from surfing to sandcastles, swimming, and everything in between.The OC is a huge center for arts and culture, with significant artists, musicians, and celebrities calling this county home. Huntington Beach, for instance, is considered one of the top surfing destinations in the world.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolo