&nbsp;', 'Raleigh, North Carolina is known for its vibrant arts and culture scene, as well as its rich history. The city is home to a number of museums, art galleries, and historical landmarks. Raleigh is also known for its foodie culture, with a number of top-rated restaurants and food trucks. And, of course, no visit to Raleigh would be complete without taking in a game or two at the famed Raleigh Sportsplex.&nbsp;Check out Raleigh’s award-winning restaurants, cool cafes, breweries, bars, world-class museums, and festivals.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e3ee86f300d0_raleigh-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e3d98ff300cb_raleigh-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/raleigh-about-banner.jpg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e383d1f300d1_raleigh-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e33cb8f300cd_raleigh-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e3b186f300d6_raleigh-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e3d81ef300ce_raleigh-getting.jpeg','<p id="">Getting around Raleigh is very easy to do. The city offers a public transportation system with buses and trollies. Also, taxis, Uber, and Lyft are all also available options.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e35d47f300cc_raleigh-fnb.jpeg','<p id="">Raleigh has a variety of restaurants, bars, and breweries, so whether you’re looking for a casual meal or a night out on the town, Raleigh has you covered.Some of Raleigh’s most popular restaurants include The Pit BBQ, Buku Global Street Food, and The Rockford. If you have time, make a reservation at Gravy This place serves Italian-American fare made fresh with local ingredients served in a beautiful, cozy atmosphere.If you’re looking for a night out, check out some of Raleigh’s bars and clubs like the Boxcar Bar + Arcade or the Lincoln Theatre. For those who prefer to spend their time outdoors, Raleigh also has a number of parks and trails that are perfect for a picnic.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d07791c3e3f059f300d5_raleigh-facts.jpeg','<p id="">The population of Raleigh is 475,000 residents.The climate in Raleigh is continental. Winters are wet and cold, and the summers are hot and humid.Raleigh is the only state capital that was planned.The capital building in Raleigh was originally built as a tomb.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Attraction Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irur