&nbsp;', 'It’s no wonder that they call Rochester the Flower City, as it is home to the Strong Museum’s indoor year-round butterfly garden. While the city does have its quirks, visitors will find that this beautifully unique area, part of the Finger Lakes region, has much to offer its visitors by way of food, activities, artistic venues, and adventures. Check out the historic architecture, boat Lake Ontario, or find your way to one of the many museums that call this old city home.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894ce53a64b60c_rochester-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894c749964b60a_rochester-c2.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63ca0aabed101e2274342f82_63c9ddb96dddae08d0ac69a8_63c9d6500c3d4b2fbeda7ac6_ExploroAd.jpeg', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/rochester-about-banner_0.jpg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894c5a7864b609_rochester-overview_0.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894c4d0a64b608_rochester-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894c76a164b607_rochester-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894c4cf264b60b_rochester-getting_0.jpeg','<p id="">Some say that a car is a necessity for getting around Rochester. Although true most of the time, those who are willing can see a lot of attractions up close on foot or bicycle. Otherwise, you can take advantage of the municipal bus system, which is only about $5 for a day pass.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0774c894c7c1164b60d_rochester-fnb_0.jpeg','<p id="">Dining in Rochester is typical of most mid-sized American cities. While parts of the immediate suburbs are teeming with large chain restaurants, many of Rochester’s surrounding villages boast a variety of family-owned establishments.And with the city’s vibrant nightlife scene, there are plenty of places to enjoy a refreshing cocktail or two.Whether you’re looking for a quick bite or a leisurely meal, Rochester has something to offer. From gastropubs to fine dining, you’ll find plenty of options to suit your taste. And with the city’s many farmers markets and food festivals, you’re sure to find fresh, local produce to enjoy.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d069c9d419ab105001d9_cancun-facts_0.jpeg','<p id="">Colonel Nathanial Rochester founded Rochester in 1817.In 1906, Xerox was founded in Rochester as the "Haloid Photographic Company."In 1888, nurserymen George Ellwanger and Patrick Barry endowed the Rochester community with 20 acres of land, now Highland Park. It is one of the nation’s first municipal arboretums.A statue of Frederick Douglass overlooks the arena in Highland Park.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Attraction Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt 