Santo Domingo is the capital city of the Dominican Republic, the largest city in the country, and the most populated city in the Caribbean. It’s a great place to travel if you’re looking for a mix of history, culture, and fun in the sun. The city is home to some of the oldest buildings in the Americas, as well as some of the best beaches in the Caribbean. And, of course, there’s plenty of rum and cigars to enjoy while you’re here, as well as natural attractions to explore with the whole family.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5c510eb856c4_santo-domingo-c1_0.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5ce5c0b856c2_santo-domingo-c2_0.jpeg', '', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/santo-domingo.mp4', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5cb258b856c6_santo-domingo-overview_0.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5cfca7b856c0_santo-domingo-c3_0.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5c551fb856c5_santo-domingo-c4_0.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5c8826b856c1_santo-domingo-getting_0.jpeg','<p id="">Tourists can navigate most of the Santo Domingo area on foot or by bike, and a subway with two lines will transport visitors to key tourist areas. Ride-share apps like Uber and Cabify are also available for attractions located further out.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5ce6e8b856c3_santo-domingo-fnb.jpeg','<p id="">The food and drink scene in Santo Domingo is one of the liveliest and most vibrant in the Caribbean. Spanish, African, and indigenous Taino cuisines influence the flavors of the Dominican. When sampling a local dish, expect it to be full of herbs and spices. Asian influences are also seen throughout the city, as one of only 3 Chinatowns in the Caribbean is found here in Santo Domingo.And, of course, there are plenty of places to enjoy a refreshing cocktail or an ice-cold beer.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d0980bec5c4808b856c7_santo-domingo-facts.jpeg','<p id="">Santo Domingo has the oldest inhabited European settlement in the Americas The city is situated right on the coast, containing the busiest port in the Dominican Republic. Visit the city to see for yourself how critical a role history plays to tourism and local industries.The city comes alive at night with multiple restaurants, cafes, and bars located in the city center. Santo Domingo is one of the most developed in the Dominican Republic.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Restaurant Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum'], ARRAY['Attraction Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nul