Tromso is one of the fastest growing cities, with a population increase of 14.4% over the last ten years. Tromso is the largest fishing port in North Norway and the world’s largest center for arctic education. Tourism in Tromso began to explode after Joanna Lumley of the BBC featured the city in her series "The Land of the Northern lights."

Since then, the municipality welcomes visitors year round and offers magnificent views and an excellent food scene.', 'Tromso is a city in the northern part of Norway that is a major administrative center and cultural hub north of the arctic circle. Like all population centers in this region, Tromso is a top destination for residents and guests looking to see the Northern Lights. The historic center of Tromso is distinguished by antique wooden houses that are hundreds of years old. In 1965, the Arctic Cathedral was completed. Today, it is famous for its unique architecture, pointed roof, and soaring stained-glass windows. Both of these attractions bring in hundreds of visitors to Tromso each year.', '', '', '', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/tromso-norway.mp4', ARRAY['','',''], ARRAY['','<p id="">Tromso has an excellent public transportation system with clean, modern buses that run on schedule. You can reach any destination you want to visit by bus, but there are also taxis and rental cars available.</p>'], ARRAY['','<p id="">Because it is a larger municipality, Tromso has many great restaurants that offer meals from around the world and traditional Norwegian cuisine. While in Tromso, we suggest trying the national dish, Farikal, which is a mutton and cabbage stew.</p>'], ARRAY['','<p id="">The official language of Tromso is Norwegian, but most residents speak English as a second language.The climate in Tromso is tundra/arctic. The winters are long, cold, and wet, and the summers are brief, warm, and dry.Tromso is considered a great place to see the Northern Lights.Tromso has a population of 71,500.The currency in Tromso is the Norwegian Krone.</p>'], ARRAY['Hotel Tab Heading','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in volu