Recent history traced its roots to 1498, when Portuguese explorer Vasco da Gama landed on Zanzibar. Today, Zanzibar is considered a great beach destination and a good value. The city contains culture, colorful character, rich history, and unique architecture. The beautiful white sand beaches and the calm, blue water offer plenty of opportunities for relaxing, snorkeling, fishing, and scuba diving.', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08134ed2605da1c6d1c_zanzibar-c1.jpeg', 'https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08134ed267ddc1c6d18_zanzibar-c2.jpeg', '', 'https://media-dev.exploro.com/inflight-media/zanzibar-about-banner.jpg', ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08234ed26442a1c6d34_zanzibar-overview.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08134ed26444a1c6d1e_zanzibar-c3.jpeg','https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08134ed26a4d11c6d19_zanzibar-c4.jpeg'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08134ed26dbdf1c6d1a_zanzibar-getting.jpeg','<p id="">Like other African cities, most visitors arrive in Zanzibar by air, rail, or bus. Many attractions are just a walk away, while some require transportation.One of the best options is to hire a moto, a two-wheeled open-air cart pulled by a motorcycle. These are popular and less expensive, making it possible to see more of the city. Taxis are an option, but agreeing on a price before starting your ride is essential. Rental cars are also available, but this option can be expensive.</p>'], ARRAY['https://uploads-ssl.webflow.com/63be358a2ba7e25fed479661/63c8d08134ed2647291c6d1d_zanzibar-fnb.jpeg','<p id="">Many people come to Zanzibar to kick back on the beautifulbeaches and get some sun. They find that after relaxation, the best thing to do is try some Zanzibar cuisine like Mishkaki, which consists of chicken, fish, and mutton placed on a skewer and cooked on a grill. 